    'bio' => 'Joe Marenda is a Partner and the Head of Digital Assets Research and Head of Hedge Fund Research at Cambridge Associates, LLC. Since joining the firm in 2006, Joe has been instrumental in advancing the firm’s focus on alternative assets and launched the firm’s Digital Assets initiative in 2018. He leads a global team of thirteen professionals across five offices. Cambridge manages approximately $80 billion in hedge fund assets.

