    'bio' => 'Amar Kuchinad serves as the Global CEO of Copper.co, a leading digital asset infrastructure provider offering custody, prime services, and settlement solutions. With a diverse background spanning traditional finance and fintech innovation, Amar brings a wealth of experience to drive Copper\'s institutional-first approach.
