At Trumid Financial, Amar took on the role of Chief Strategy Officer, overseeing the company\'s strategic direction for its electronic corporate bond marketplace. Most recently, he served as a Senior Managing Director at Pretium Partners, an alternative asset manager with over $50 billion in AUM, where he was responsible for technology, data, analytics, and risk across the management company and its operating subsidiaries.',
